    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You channel all your stored energy into your fist before slamming it into your enemy's core, with the force of a meteor. Make a Melee Taijutsu attack against a target creature in range. On a hit your deal twice your [weapons damage] + Xd12 fire damage where X equals your current Fury stacks and force the target creature to make a Strength Saving throw to avoid be knocked prone and restrained into the ground until the start of their next turn</p>",
